DBZ Coin Use Case

The Diamond Boyz Coin ongoing development plan is to use the $DBZ coin as the native token when swapping for NFT's. The initial use of the NFT's will be to create "Diamond Swap" a custom coded ticketing marketplace with a series of concerts (aka NFT collections) using performers who are also current clients.

As the coin and technology grows it will also be used when building our own Blockchain called the "Diamond Chain" that is much more complex and will help to facilitate jewelry transactions.

Why DBZ Coin

The Coin

Diamond Boyz Coin is built on cryptocurrency “Blockchain” technology that is immutable and non-reversible. These features prevent fraud and backcharges on payments. Also The DBZ transaction ledger is public, dating back to the genesis date. The DBZ ledger is based on the https://www.bscscan.com website by searching the contract address exactly.

The Entertainment

#DBZ gives users access to premier posts, comments, videos, and more. The Diamond Boyz hope to help users not only through the Token Smart Contract process but also to guide them to the latest social media platforms such as Instagram, Facebook, Twitter, Tik Tok, the list goes on and on!

Efficient Transfers

Using the most up to date blockchain technology, transfers and smart contracts can be deployed in seconds. These key features allow users to obtain target funds quickly and creates a more efficient monetary system worldwide.

Well Known

Some of the faces behind Diamond Boyz have been growing their own brands for years in various ways. Mainly, the legend himself, Johnny Dang, hopes to share his experiences through Diamond Boyz Coin by signing up users worldwide to new platforms.

The Diamond Boyz Coin

Is Not An ICO Token. Is Not An Exchange. DBZ was released publicly on it’s genesis date where it was immediately available to the world. The Diamond Boyz Coin is in no way an exchange and generally offers a knowledge base on how to interact with a selected Smart Contract. The knowledge shared can be applied to any Smart Contract and is at the full disposal of the community.

Security Measures

The Diamond Boyz Coin source code is publicly available when searching the token address on https://www.bscscan.com and has gone through several security audits prior it's genesis date. More audits will continue to be done as our holder count grows.

Mission

DBZ Coin aims to become the leader in payment and verification for authentic jewelry purchases as well as set a standard for a faster remittance systems worldwide. By walking users through how to obtain Diamond Boyz Coin, is also introducing them to a new way to interact with the internet in an entertaining and valuable way.
